<h1>OpenOil API</h1>

<h2> Features common to all requests </h2>

The <b>root url</b> is <b>http://api.openoil.net/</b>. You can optionally specify a version number in the URL -- <b>http://api.openoil.net/v0.1</b>. Requests which do not specify a version number will be redirected to the latest version.

You can control paging in any request:
<ul>
  <li><b>page</b>: page number of results to show. First page is 1</li>
  <li><b>per_page</b>: number of results to fetch</li>
</ul>


<h2>Concessions</h2>

