You can limit the results by any of:

<ul>
  <li><b>country</b>: 2-letter country code</li>
  <li><b>type</b>: one of <i>offshore, onshore</i></li>
  <li><b>status</b>: one of <i>licensed, unlicensed</i></li>
</ul>

For example, you can find all licensed concession areas in Australia with:

<blockquote><code>
